        "text_twGGkJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Skin that's mostly comfortable, neither tight nor shiny, and doesn't ask for much. Balanced skin is the most tolerant type and the least prone to trouble. This is also where most combination skin sits, a little oilier through the T-zone and a little drier on the cheeks. The job here isn't to fix anything. It's to keep a good thing good.</p>",
            "width": "fit-content",
            "max_width": "normal",
            "alignment": "left",
            "type_preset": "rte",
            "font": "var(--font-primary--family)",
            "font_size": "",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "normal",
            "case": "none",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "text_color": "",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
            "corner_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "text_AkCqgY": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Is this you?</p>",
            "width": "fit-content",
            "max_width": "normal",
            "alignment": "left",
            "type_preset": "h3",
            "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
            "font_size": "1rem",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "normal",
            "case": "none",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "text_color": "",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
            "corner_radius": 0,
